entry.value: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS default.${kudu_table_name} ( `id` STRING NOT NULL, `version` STRING NULL, `timestamp` STRING NULL, `certainty` STRING NULL, `type` STRING NULL, `subtype` STRING NULL, `eventannotation` STRING NULL, `source` STRING NULL, `latitude` DOUBLE NULL, `longitude` DOUBLE NULL, `payload` STRING NULL, `attributes` STRING NULL, PRIMARY KEY (id)) PARTITION BY HASH (id) PARTITIONS 8 STORED AS KUDU TBLPROPERTIES ('kudu.master_addresses'='master:7051', 'kudu.table_name'='${kudu_table_name}')
